          "metadata": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**`22. Carte simple X–Y colorée par taux`**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "nF6h9EgIYh3i"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "plt.figure(figsize=(8,8))\n",
        "plt.scatter(df[\"X\"], df[\"Y\"], c=df[\"Taux_Chlordecone\"], cmap=\"Reds\", s=10)\n",
        "plt.colorbar(label=\"Taux de chlordécone\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Carte des parcelles contaminées\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"X\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Y\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 719
        },
        "id": "6WIiYA3qWjWL",
        "outputId": "36a397c4-5226-40e9-e3d8-70c26061976e"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "<Figure size 800x800 with 2 Axes>"
            ],
            "image/png": "\n"
          },
          "metadata": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**`Interprétation`**\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "La carte révèle une forte hétérogénéité spatiale.\n",
        "Les points rouges foncés (forte contamination) se concentrent dans :\n",
        "\n",
        "le Nord Atlantique (Morne-Rouge, Macouba, Grand’Rivière),\n",
        "\n",
        "certaines zones de Sainte-Marie et Trinité.\n",
        "\n",
        "Les zones du Sud et du Centre montrent une contamination faible à très faible.\n",
        "\n",
        "Cette carte confirme que la contamination est géographiquement structurée, en lien avec :\n",
        "\n",
        "l’histoire agricole (bananeraies),\n",
        "\n",
        "la nature des sols,\n",
        "\n",
        "la topographie."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "zIGkwZa4Qarr"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "plt.tight_layout()\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 34
        },
        "id": "hTHZTVVFOY1z",
        "outputId": "00672a71-ae8a-41fe-857c-5d2b0576555a"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "<Figure size 640x480 with 0 Axes>"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**`23. Préparation des données pour ACP / clustering`**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "HPrjlrcKYrF_"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "features = [\"Taux_Chlordecone\"] + topo_cols\n",
        "X = df[features].dropna()\n",
        "\n",
        "scaler = StandardScaler()\n",
        "X_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(X)\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "x0a9A-HnYhOB"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**`24. ACP sur variables topographiques + contamination`**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "iIQkdX4rYzUb"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "pca = PCA(n_components=2)\n",
        "pca_res = pca.fit_transform(X_scaled)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(6,5))\n",
        "plt.scatter(pca_res[:,0], pca_res[:,1], c=X[\"Taux_Chlordecone\"], cmap=\"viridis\", s=10)\n",
        "plt.colorbar(label=\"Taux de chlordécone\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"ACP – topographie + contamination\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"PC1\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"PC2\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 487
        },
        "id": "Iq_LLtbpYhKb",
        "outputId": "d2610072-886b-4a4a-dec1-919828df3d9d"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "<Figure size 600x500 with 2 Axes>"
            ],
            "image/png": "\n"
          },
          "metadata": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**`Interprétation`**\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "L’ACP montre que :\n",
        "\n",
        "Le premier axe (PC1) est fortement lié à la pente, la rugosité et l’exposition.\n",
        "Il oppose les zones plates aux zones accidentées.\n",
        "\n",
        "Le second axe (PC2) est influencé par le TPI et l’ombrage, reflétant la position relative dans le relief (crêtes, pentes, vallées).\n",
        "\n",
        "Les parcelles fortement contaminées se regroupent dans une zone spécifique du plan factoriel, ce qui suggère que la topographie influence la rétention du chlordécone.\n",
        "\n",
        "Les zones plates, humides et peu drainées semblent favoriser l’accumulation."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "hLLfff-jQlhm"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "plt.tight_layout()\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 34
        },
        "id": "mUOOrTsQObZW",
        "outputId": "6bc4b619-12e1-4fcd-ae48-67adf6ab4a2f"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "<Figure size 640x480 with 0 Axes>"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**`25. Clustering K-means`**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "4vYMsw8aY9Z8"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=4, random_state=42)\n",
        "clusters = kmeans.fit_predict(X_scaled)\n",
        "df.loc[X.index, \"cluster_topo\"] = clusters\n",
        "df[\"cluster_topo\"].value_counts()\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 241
        },
        "id": "uCFoV7cWYhHl",
        "outputId": "a01562eb-6de1-451f-cba8-15d63cf84728"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "cluster_topo\n",
              "1.0    13685\n",
              "2.0     8075\n",
              "0.0     7971\n",
              "3.0     1359\n",
              "Name: count, dtype: int64"
            ],
            "text/html": [
              "<div>\n",
              "<style scoped>\n",
              "    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n",
              "        vertical-align: middle;\n",
